Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.03,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,{\i1}Basmele sunt așa niște prostii.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.63,0:00:23.84,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mereu este vorba despre o fată peste care e aruncată o vrajă și e transformată într-o prințesă,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:25.96,Default,ninny,0,0,0,,{\i1}ajunge să poarte o rochie frumoasă
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:28.15,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,{\i1}și alege un băiat drăguț care se îndrăgostește și el de ea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:32.13,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,{\i1}Să nu mai spun că vraja se rupe atunci când ți-e lumea mai dragă. E o prostie totală, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:31.01,Default,Paparazzi A,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uitați-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:32.13,Default,Papapazzi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Este Ninny!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bună, Ninny!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:36.39,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,{\i1}Și totusi, dintr-un oarecare motiv, toate fetele vor sa fie prințese.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:36.39,Default,Paparazzi A,0,0,0,,{\an8}Drăguț hanorac!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.47,Default,Paparazzi A,0,0,0,,{\an8}Este adevărat că te-ai despărțit de TJ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:40.64,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,{\i1}Adică, pe bune? Vraja se rupe așa dintr-odată.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:40.22,Default,Paparazzi B,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nu v-am mai văzut împreună de ceva timp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:43.03,Default,Paparazzi C,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ți-ai găsit pe altcineva?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:43.56,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asta era inevitabil deoarece ți-ai încălcat promisiunea?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:44.89,Default,Paparazzi D,0,0,0,,{\an8}Haide, dă-ne câteva detalii.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:46.06,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sau deoarece timpul s-a scurs, deci nu poți face nimic?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:47.15,Default,Paparazzi D,0,0,0,,{\an8}Am auzit că cineva a părăsit grupul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:47.90,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,{\i0}Dar {\i1}poți{\i0} face ceva.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.75,Default,Paparazzi C,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ce părere ai de pierderea unui membru?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:51.46,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sunteți cu toții niște proști.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:52.82,Default,Paparazzi E,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nu te înțelegeai cu Macy, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:55.32,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,{\i1}Niciunul din voi nu știe adevăratul motiv pentru care se rupe vraja.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:53.99,Default,Paparazzi E,0,0,0,,{\an8}A fost așa mereu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:55.86,Default,Paparazzi B,0,0,0,,{\an8}Acesta este motivul?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:58.16,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Cât de enervanți.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:00:59.32,Default,Paparazzi A,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.11,0:01:05.89,Default,Paparazzi A,0,0,0,,Hei, așteaptă! Ninny!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:08.13,Default,Paparazzi B,0,0,0,,Ce naiba a fost acea lumină?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:22.74,Default,Paparazzi,0,0,0,,A luat-o pe acea alee!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:25.92,Default,Paparazzi A,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,0:01:29.08,Default,Paparazzi B,0,0,0,,A dispărut...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:32.61,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dacă magie funcționează doar pe proști,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:37.59,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,{\i1}atunci prefer ca eu să fiu cea care aruncă vraja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:46.71,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Vârful degetului meu este granița vocii mele.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:49.33,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Cheia de Fier a lui Joe Răzbunătorul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:52.09,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Five locks, three chains, silence-sheathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.21,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,A blast from the pipe to blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:03.97,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Te rog să nu-ți folosești magia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:07.22,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Asta îți va face coarnele... să înflorească...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:13.07,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Scânteia Albastră!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:25.79,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Magic Number 44: Flash Bumper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.24,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,A fost cât pe ce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:33.77,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Acela este un cerb cu muguri, știi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:37.11,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,That's an A-rank harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:40.43,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Ce ai fi făcut dacă nu aș fi ajuns la timp?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:45.68,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Nu vreau să aud asta de la cineva care ajunge incredibil de târziu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:46.94,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Ninny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:52.19,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Ți-am zis să nu-mi mai spui pe prenume! Sunt mai mare ca tine, deci arată-mi puțin respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:53.41,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Niiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:59.72,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dacă vei începe să-mi spui "Noel", mă voi gândi la asta, Ninny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:03.49,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Where do you get off casually making \Ndemands of your seniors like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:08.57,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dragonii: ființe mitice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:13.50,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dar adevărul este că nu sunt nici mitice și nici ființe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:20.16,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}Încă din vremuri străvechi, 72% din decesele din Londra
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:24.01,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}erau provocate de creaturi grotești cunoscute ca dragoni.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:30.25,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}De asta sunt afișate atât de strident pe stema Londrei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:34.37,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dragonii scăpați de sub control produc mult rău oamenilor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:40.06,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ca să se prevină acest lucru, dragonii trebuiesc monitorizați.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:45.26,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cetățenii Londrei de Suprafață nu pot vedea dragonii.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:49.83,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dar există și Londra Răstunată.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:56.04,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doar cei care trăiesc pe partea răstunată a Londrei pot vedea dragonii.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:04:04.85,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Inevital, grija dragonilor a picat pe oamenii din Londra Răsturnată.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:07.18,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ce naiba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:12.81,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,You guys still haven't fixed this from\Nwhen that big guy wrecked it? Jalnic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:15.06,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,N-Ne pare rău...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.82,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,We were asked to get the monitor up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:23.12,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Și tu! Tu de ce te-ai apucat să faci o misiune de două persoane de una singură?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:25.11,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Deoarece tu ai întârziat, Ninny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.70,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Majoritatea oamenilor ar fi așteptat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:33.58,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Dacă aș fi dus-o la bun sfârșit de una singură, toată răsplata ar fi fost a mea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:34.24,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Știam eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:36.75,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Deci asta urmăreai tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:40.01,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,You make plenty at your job in Front London,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:42.56,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,so just exchange as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:46.34,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I have {\i1}some{\i0} pride, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.62,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,And quit saying stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:50.60,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:53.47,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,I lost achievement points.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:57.35,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,But I plucked all the flowers that\Nbloomed so they wouldn't find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:05:00.66,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Yes! I got points!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:01.99,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:06.29,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Because of my assist at the end, duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:08.94,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,That's the only reason our\Npayload made it out safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.81,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:12.83,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.64,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,They'll be pissed if they catch \Nyou sneaking photos again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.12,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:20.71,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Why are you plucking flowers \Noff of bud bucks, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.63,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Well, what was I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:26.88,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,They go down in price if their \Nflowers bloom before they're sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:29.11,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,I did it for our client.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.75,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,See? Isn't it pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:34.89,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,You can touch it if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:36.72,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,You can't have it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.69,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,A-As if I'd want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:41.68,Default,Osushi,0,0,0,,Let me see your panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:45.81,Default,Osushi,0,0,0,,Let me see your panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:50.67,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Hey! Osushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.67,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What's that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:51.78,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Is it a dark dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:54.59,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,In the middle of the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:55.79,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:56.95,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,It's just Balgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.79,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Damn it. Not him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:03.92,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Osushi! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:10.05,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,You're a cutie! You're absolutely \Nadorable, so please, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:13.31,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Balgo and Osushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:14.93,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Indeed it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:19.21,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,So do something about them. \NYou're in charge of them, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:22.57,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're{\i0} in charge of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.94,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,He's your senior at school, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.95,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,I mean, it's probably fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:32.07,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Look. He's all smiles.\NWhy don't we have some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.54,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I want a caffè latte.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.78,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,I'll be glad to push the button,\Nbut you have to put the money in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:41.44,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,There's nothing "fine" about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:44.34,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,At this rate, Balgo's going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:49.97,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,We've been tasked with keeping an eye\Non him, so I need you two to do your jobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.89,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Getting us to keep tabs on dragonclads
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:57.60,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,is basically HQ's way of making\Nthis nonsense our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:02.28,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,It's not like we get paid\Nor earn achievement points
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:04.23,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,for keeping him out of trouble 24/7
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.29,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,while we're on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:09.41,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,So we're back to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.99,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,I figured you might say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.73,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,So I talked to some of the higher-ups
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:19.20,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,and got you girls some extra money\Nand achievement points for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.23,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:24.84,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,All right, fine. Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.75,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Let's go, Niiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.63,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,You're doing this for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.49,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I'm doing it for merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:36.26,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,But just so we don't sound completely\Nawful, we're doing it for society!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:44.58,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,Could you maybe shout the\N"doing it for society" part first?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:52.42,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:55.51,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Osushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:59.11,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Well, if you say so, Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:04.17,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,You're such a good doggie, Osushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:07.66,Default,Random lady,0,0,0,,It sure is noisy over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:11.55,Default,Jimmy,0,0,0,,Yeah. Maybe there's a dragon on the loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:15.63,Default,Random lady,0,0,0,,Don't even joke about that.\NMake sure it's spick and span up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:17.05,Default,Jimmy,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.68,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.19,Default,Jimmy,0,0,0,,Balgo, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.32,Default,Jimmy,0,0,0,,Don't come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:36.70,Default,Random lady,0,0,0,,Goodness, that chimney\Nsweep's really going at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.20,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Sorry! I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.83,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.61,Default,Jimmy,0,0,0,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:47.84,Default,Jimmy,0,0,0,,I'm not hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:52.34,Default,Jimmy,0,0,0,,I just don't wanna get arrested for \Nviolating the dragon contact law!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:56.23,Default,Jimmy,0,0,0,,Wing Bind HQ is right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:04.63,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.24,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:10.11,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I'm the one who saved you, you dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:15.32,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,There, there. Please calm down, Osushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:19.84,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Osushi's calm now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:23.55,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,What did you do to the poor thing, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:26.75,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Nothing. I was just taking Osushi for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:30.23,Default,Jimmy,0,0,0,,Uh... Thank you, witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:34.17,Default,Jimmy,0,0,0,,So, um... about that chimney...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:37.76,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Your dragon insurance should cover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.51,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:41.93,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Did you come into contact with the dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:45.39,Default,Jimmy,0,0,0,,N-No! Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.38,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Niiha, run the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:48.65,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:51.61,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Please lick this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:56.90,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Um... What happens if \Nsomeone touches a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:00.66,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,For the protection of both \Ndragons and humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:05.76,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,the Dragon Contact Prohibition\NLaw was passed in 1609.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.29,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Violators face 100 years in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:10.04,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.53,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,They get executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:13.66,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:18.30,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,It's within the normal range.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:23.18,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:24.66,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,This is all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.18,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.77,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Who do you think... {\alpha&HFF&}caused...\Nthis mess... in the first place... huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:28.94,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Who do you think... caused...{\alpha&HFF&}\Nthis mess... in the first place... huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.59,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.31,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Who do you think... caused...\Nthis mess... {\alpha&HFF&}in the first place... huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:31.69,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Who do you think... caused...\Nthis mess... in the first place... {\alpha&HFF&}huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:31.85,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:32.19,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Who do you think... caused...\Nthis mess... in the first place... huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:36.44,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Also, why don't you put a muzzle \Non Osushi when you go out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:39.58,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,You're the only civilian who can\Ntouch Osushi and not get locked up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:41.96,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,because you're a dragonclad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:43.20,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Do you realize that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.99,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,But I did put one on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:50.27,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,It just got ripped off when Osushi suddenly \Nsprouted wings while we were walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.69,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Did Osushi really grow wings \Nwithout anything triggering it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:56.21,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.56,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Where did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.67,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.26,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Please try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.96,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Osushi's wings usually appear
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:10.79,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,when you try to bark like Osushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.39,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,or when you sneeze,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:15.98,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,or when you start cracking up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.11,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,So all the time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:19.55,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:23.40,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,when you're in danger, Balgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.12,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,It would appear that, as a dragonclad,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.97,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,you aggressively attract\N dragons toward you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:41.08,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,For now, I need you to take Osushi and get\Nsomewhere where there aren't many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:44.89,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Ninny, the barrier tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:46.26,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:52.32,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,So what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:57.90,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Magic Number 04: Stun Ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.51,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Wait! What was the point of the barrier tape?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.51,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.50,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Oh, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:17.75,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,We've subdued a dragon,\Nso if we could get a bonus...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:20.45,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Dragon insurance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:26.10,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,No, that's not our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:29.64,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Please stop whining. It's quite pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.90,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you don't know what kind of dragon it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:35.31,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:38.18,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've seen one like it,\Nso I don't know what kind it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:44.91,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,It was rather worked up, \Nso I stunned it to shut it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.28,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Niiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.89,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,It just went lights out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.14,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:16.01,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,We need to get it away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:16.82,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:31.03,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,All right, this should be good—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:34.75,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. You're making\N this really difficult to call in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.14,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Ninny, in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:52.56,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.30,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Rutherford Street. We need \Nan emergency dragon blockade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:57.95,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,We've got a dark dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:10.90,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:12.77,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:23.18,Default,Broadcast,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}This is a notice from BBC Reverse London.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:26.38,Default,Broadcast,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Due to a dark dragon alert,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:30.23,Default,Broadcast,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Rutherford Street is now\Nunder a dragon blockade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:36.07,Default,Broadcast,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Anyone in the vicinity should\Nseek shelter immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:40.39,Default,Broadcast,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Wing Bind has the situation under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:42.15,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,You know what always gets me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:47.80,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Doesn't it just piss you off when they say,\N"Wing Bind has the situation under control"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:50.88,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,No, because it's our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:51.95,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:54.95,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I'd be fine with it if we said it ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:57.57,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,but why's the BBC announcing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:03.46,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Chief, the dragon blockade is set up, \Nso it's time we switched out with the Sabres—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:07.21,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh, hello? Noel? Hello—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:09.97,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:14.44,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,That's my line. You were really going \Nto let the Sabres take all the credit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:22.98,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,This is our chance to show\NHR how powerful we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:27.62,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Our duty as Pipers is to take dragons \Nto pasture and harvest from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:28.99,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,We don't need to be powerful—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.79,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Like I said before...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:35.49,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I want to join the Sabres!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.96,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Well, personally, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:55.72,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:57.43,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:02.10,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Magic Number 28: Rainy Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.45,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:18.75,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Balgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.67,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:31.45,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Magic Number 75: Gatling Crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.77,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Hey. This is a huge deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.77,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,How many years has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:43.99,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,It's been a century!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.86,Default,Roy,0,0,0,,Ninety-six years, to be precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:48.35,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,That's basically a century!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:55.41,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,A whole century since the last time we let \Na dark dragon get into Reverse London!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.07,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,If this isn't a catastrophe, what the hell {\i1}is{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.45,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Could you show up for once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:02.89,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Stop chewing gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:06.21,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,You guys seriously have nothin' to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:09.13,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Am I the only one upset here? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.79,Default,Roy,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:20.24,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Anyway, my point is, letting this\NBalgo guy run around is the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:23.47,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,What do you say, Old Man Wolfy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:30.43,Default,Wolfgang,0,0,0,,{\an8}He has been the topic of countless \Ndiscussions within our squad
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:33.90,Default,Wolfgang,0,0,0,,{\an8}in the month since he became a dragonclad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:38.24,Default,Wolfgang,0,0,0,,This situation occurred \Ndue to our own negligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:41.18,Default,Wolfgang,0,0,0,,We cannot simply ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:47.71,Default,Wolfgang,0,0,0,,We will proceed with the plan to eliminate\Nthe dragonclad known as Balgo Parks.
